               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18431023-name-144" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18431023-name-144" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18431023-name-144" type="surname" value="PETERKIN"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18431023-name-144" type="given" value="HENRY JOHN"></interp>HENRY JOHN PETERKIN</persName>
                  </hi>. I live in High-street, Poplar, and am a printer. On the 23rd of Sept. I was at my shop window, and saw the prisoner go into Mr. Abbott's shop, opposite mine, lift a shawl off the line inside the shop, and put it under his coat—I crossed over, and said, "Where is that shawl?"—he immediately ran away—I pursued, calling "Stop thief"—he was stopped about fifty yards off—I saw him throw the shawl on a wall—I took it down.</p>
